originalText.text: Justin is exactly what I’ve been looking for in a guitar teacher: knowledgeable, patient, and attentive, with an approach that brings the guitar to life as an instrument. With a jazz education and dexterity in many styles, Justin takes my musical interests into account and seamlessly incorporates ear training and theory into our lessons. What makes this so great? Instead of mindlessly aping tab, I’m gaining a feel for the sound and logic of the guitar itself. My ears and hands are getting to know the guitar and so gain skills for coaxing the sounds and songs I want out of it— and that’s why I wanted to take lessons in the first place. Besides the efficacy of his method, Justin is reliable and professional as a teacher, giving you his undivided attention as you learn together. If you’ve also been looking for a guitar teacher who not only has chops but is interested in helping you develop musically, I can’t recommend Justin highly enough.
